大學學位個d會唔同d<br />\n但係讀<span style=\"color: red;\">hd</span>，fd個班出黎一定係做垃圾職位<br />\n而你一開始做得垃圾職位，起碼等十幾年廿年先有得升d好嘅職位，因為酒店老屎忽實在太多<br />\n所以話曬鳩人十萬八萬學費</blockquote><br />\n讀HD有邊行唔係咁?</blockquote><br />\nit n展嘅hd一畢業人工高好多"},{"pid":"69a6397f9493aa81803b9a9b9df2761dea83ac58","tid":324991,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪由低做起囉 你有能力既 好快都會上到位 成日咁短視 只會愈黎愈辛苦同頹 共勉呀巴打💪💪</blockquote><br />\n有時唔係有能力就有得升<br />\n咁多老屎忽係到<br />\n等三四十歲先啦"},{"pid":"43875db0b2a507bed03253118cf960f5fca271f0","tid":324991,"uid":11258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:24:46.000Z","msg":"讀酒店唔做酒店得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0126dd93963ae07b5ca74b3d86f40e10b85520ee","tid":324991,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇人, 係冇能力ge咪由低做起<br />\n識有人一grad就做hotel manager <br />\n人地4年大學付出左幾多你又知?</blockquote><br />\n有大學學位個d會唔同d<br />\n但係讀<span style=\"color: red;\">hd</span>，fd個班出黎一定係做垃圾職位<br />\n而你一開始做得垃圾職位，起碼等十幾年廿年先有得升d好嘅職位，因為酒店老屎忽實在太多<br />\n所以話曬鳩人十萬八萬學費</blockquote><br />\n讀HD有邊行唔係咁?</blockquote><br />\nit n展嘅hd一畢業人工高好多</blockquote><br />\nHD考唔到牌架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a491fffc4cf8903e341587fc2d6a3ed4d29c2cd","tid":324991,"uid":6557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"我讀tourism HD+top up, 酒店同旅行社都冇人請，最後做第二行，呢科係真乞食。<br />\n前線就算大酒店佢請DSE雞佢覺得冇問題，你去同佢爭叫價又高過DSE雞，自己又唔甘心咁低人工，做第二行係唯一出路"},{"pid":"d843bf90d042d29785550ce204cc77f4fa7f61c8","tid":324991,"uid":125509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:17:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁咪由低做起囉 你有能力既 好快都會上到位 成日咁短視 只會愈黎愈辛苦同頹 共勉呀巴打💪💪</blockquote><br />\n有時唔係有能力就有得升<br />\n咁多老屎忽係到<br />\n等三四十歲先啦</blockquote><br />\n我都明呀！ 但都無計 但基本上行行都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757b8fa2bd89ec5e1b66352295b33d7ab7f64c42","tid":324991,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇人, 係冇能力ge咪由低做起<br />\n識有人一grad就做hotel manager <br />\n人地4年大學付出左幾多你又知?</blockquote><br />\n吹得就吹，你老友係賓館做？"},{"pid":"21215020780550dcd5269461521d00f3470f298a","tid":324991,"uid":74738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:30:27.000Z","msg":"真係有能力既人 讀咩做咩都會有人睇得起你架喇"},{"pid":"ce8c6c6e46ea192f536728932f6232cde8fc089b","tid":324991,"uid":43309,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主係大陸狗黎(已自認)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg&h=4ed886d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係樓主之前個名-連尼住(大佬)</span></strong></span><br />\n讀垃圾OU HD，打字用拼音。<br />\n之後俾巴打圍屌，死不悔改之餘，<br />\n仲笑鳩人讀書少，唔抵得人識打拼音！<br />\n堅稱自己係土生土長嘅香港人喎~~<br />\n樓主用拼音打字證據：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU&d=pGABYCmRHTumhql11H3vy4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ef6f246a\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU</a><br />\n<br />\n日期：2017-1-10<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算識打字嗰陣都要轉channel去諗嗰個字嘅蝗語點讀，再打出嚟。<br />\n點都慢過用倉頡速成就咁諗點打好撚多<br />\n除非佢本身就係蝗語channel，又或者講慣蝗語<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg&h=ca5c499d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本係大陸仔打啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唸又窩又奔，都唔知佢打乜柒！<br />\n你全家奔緊落地獄呀支那狗！！！！！<br />\n下世咪撚再落黎香港，生生世世做中蟈人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過追擊之下，終於承認自己係支那狗，<br />\n並聲稱自己永遠都唔上LIHKG<br />\n又改名-你仲唔仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/15/233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F15%2F233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg&h=443b5ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但好景不常，經過一個月潛水又俾我見返佢！<br />\n所以只好繼續我嘅追擊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條柒頭份人極度陰險，之前開post叫雞俾人放飛機開post起人底！<br />\n<br />\n小心呢件ptgf<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n仲話叫ptgf唔係叫雞喎，你咪撚玩啦！<br />\n人地唔撚so你好出奇咩？<br />\n雞都嫌棄你賤種畜生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁多先，希望樓主真係好好守承諾，<br />\n唔好再上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>條賤種拎強姦慘劇黎講笑<br />\n聲稱要合法化強姦十點後外出嘅女人</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n你喺網上唔代表可以乜都講<br />\n你上得連登就代表你係一個人<br />\n唔該你地似返個人<br />\n認撚住條雞蟲份人係幾撚低劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc834b7d686c584d277841dcb27bb137d011827e","tid":324991,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇人, 係冇能力ge咪由低做起<br />\n識有人一grad就做hotel manager <br />\n人地4年大學付出左幾多你又知?</blockquote><br />\n有大學學位個d會唔同d<br />\n但係讀<span style=\"color: red;\">hd</span>，fd個班出黎一定係做垃圾職位<br />\n而你一開始做得垃圾職位，起碼等十幾年廿年先有得升d好嘅職位，因為酒店老屎忽實在太多<br />\n所以話曬鳩人十萬八萬學費</blockquote><br />\n讀HD有邊行唔係咁?</blockquote><br />\nit n展嘅hd一畢業人工高好多</blockquote><br />\nHD考唔到牌架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你傻架？<br />\n大把hd工程仔出黎做幾年野已經兩萬人工啦<br />\n乜撚野考唔到牌啊？"},{"pid":"d55aba64d890cc0fb2e4d22a6974071dddb49007","tid":324991,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我讀tourism HD+top up, 酒店同旅行社都冇人請，最後做第二行，呢科係真乞食。<br />\n前線就算大酒店佢請DSE雞佢覺得冇問題，你去同佢爭叫價又高過DSE雞，自己又唔甘心咁低人工，做第二行係唯一出路</blockquote><br />\n咁咪即係兩手空空無門手藝"},{"pid":"2de7d5573fd16cc1c28211cbea10932c16fcb347","tid":324991,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁咪由低做起囉 你有能力既 好快都會上到位 成日咁短視 只會愈黎愈辛苦同頹 共勉呀巴打💪💪</blockquote><br />\n有時唔係有能力就有得升<br />\n咁多老屎忽係到<br />\n等三四十歲先啦</blockquote><br />\n我都明呀！ 但都無計 但基本上行行都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，我覺得it n展個d升職加人工會比較易d"},{"pid":"69e8b47c4b79fb7c4940b6cfe35a235af87a2007","tid":324991,"uid":36770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀酒店唔做酒店得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得，點會唔得啊<br />\n不過你咁樣不如早d quit左佢出黎做嘢啦<br />\n係到曬學費學埋d將來用唔到嘅野做乜？"},{"pid":"43b927bbe49beca7bcf143fec6242fb197ea953f","tid":324991,"uid":36770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係有能力既人 讀咩做咩都會有人睇得起你架喇</blockquote><br />\n你真係天真<br />\n有d科好睇人事關係<br />\n有實力但你無人脈都照樣食屎"},{"pid":"6a6dead3498829f5ef073b6afbcd7a8f25e7fb39","tid":324991,"uid":36770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:27:11.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔需要反駁<br />\n酒店旅遊科係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公認<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>乞食科呢樣係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事實<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"800138f88495931cb63d1dfa3a70177920f66193","tid":324991,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇人, 係冇能力ge咪由低做起<br />\n識有人一grad就做hotel manager <br />\n人地4年大學付出左幾多你又知?</blockquote><br />\n一出黎做manager位...佢老豆係GM?"},{"pid":"76682f20a8a1413c1226df3f890e6ecd6421853e","tid":324991,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T18:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主係大陸狗黎(已自認)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg&h=4ed886d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係樓主之前個名-連尼住(大佬)</span></strong></span><br />\n讀垃圾OU HD，打字用拼音。<br />\n之後俾巴打圍屌，死不悔改之餘，<br />\n仲笑鳩人讀書少，唔抵得人識打拼音！<br />\n堅稱自己係土生土長嘅香港人喎~~<br />\n樓主用拼音打字證據：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU&d=pGABYCmRHTumhql11H3vy4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ef6f246a\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU</a><br />\n<br />\n日期：2017-1-10<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算識打字嗰陣都要轉channel去諗嗰個字嘅蝗語點讀，再打出嚟。<br />\n點都慢過用倉頡速成就咁諗點打好撚多<br />\n除非佢本身就係蝗語channel，又或者講慣蝗語<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg&h=ca5c499d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本係大陸仔打啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唸又窩又奔，都唔知佢打乜柒！<br />\n你全家奔緊落地獄呀支那狗！！！！！<br />\n下世咪撚再落黎香港，生生世世做中蟈人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過追擊之下，終於承認自己係支那狗，<br />\n並聲稱自己永遠都唔上LIHKG<br />\n又改名-你仲唔仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/15/233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F15%2F233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg&h=443b5ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但好景不常，經過一個月潛水又俾我見返佢！<br />\n所以只好繼續我嘅追擊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條柒頭份人極度陰險，之前開post叫雞俾人放飛機開post起人底！<br />\n<br />\n小心呢件ptgf<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n仲話叫ptgf唔係叫雞喎，你咪撚玩啦！<br />\n人地唔撚so你好出奇咩？<br />\n雞都嫌棄你賤種畜生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁多先，希望樓主真係好好守承諾，<br />\n唔好再上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>條賤種拎強姦慘劇黎講笑<br />\n聲稱要合法化強姦十點後外出嘅女人</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n你喺網上唔代表可以乜都講<br />\n你上得連登就代表你係一個人<br />\n唔該你地似返個人<br />\n認撚住條雞蟲份人係幾撚低劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把土生土長識拼音啦"}]}